        <updateDate>2022-03-21T11:01:25Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Defund de Blasio's Injection Sites Act of 2021</strong></p> <p>This bill prohibits federal funds from being made available to a state, local, tribal, or private entity that operates or controls an injection center (i.e., a medically supervised injection site) in violation of the federal statute commonly known as the Crack House Statute. The statute generally prohibits making facilities available for the purpose of unlawfully using a controlled substance. <br> </p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
